1
00:01:21,882 --> 00:01:24,162
ràng nǐ xúnshān nǐ zài zhè shuìdàjué
让 你 巡山 你 在 这 睡大觉
Why are you sleeping here and not going on patrol?

2
00:01:24,162 --> 00:01:25,242
zěnme la zěnme la
怎么 啦 怎么 啦
What's the matter?

3
00:01:25,242 --> 00:01:27,122
kuàihuí shāndòng dàwáng yào kāihuì
快回 山洞 大王 要 开会
Go back to the cave now! Our king is going to hold a meeting!

4
00:01:27,202 --> 00:01:28,122
kuài zǒu
快 走
Be quick!

5
00:01:42,162 --> 00:01:43,922
dàwáng dòng
大王 洞
Da Wang cave

6
00:01:46,002 --> 00:01:47,402
zhè shénme dōu kànbúdào a
这 什么 都 看不到 啊
I can't see anything.

7
00:01:47,402 --> 00:01:48,362
dōu guài nǐ
都 怪 你
It's all your fault.

8
00:01:48,362 --> 00:01:49,762
dàwáng chūlái le
大王 出来 了
Hear ye, hear ye. King is coming!

9
00:01:49,762 --> 00:01:52,962
xiǎo de men gàosù dàjiā yígè hǎoxiāoxī
小 的 们 告诉 大家 一个 好消息
Listen! My little ones, here is a big good news!

10
00:01:53,402 --> 00:01:56,402
wǔtiān hòu tángsēng shītú sìrényào jīngguò cǐdì
五天 后 唐僧 师徒 四人要 经过 此地
Tang Monk and his three disciples will pass through here in five days.

11
00:01:56,402 --> 00:01:57,322
wa
哇
Yeah! Yeah!

12
00:01:57,562 --> 00:01:58,882
tángsēng tángsēng shì shuí
唐僧 唐僧 是 谁
Tang Monk? Who is it?

13
00:01:58,882 --> 00:02:00,442
tángsēng nǐ dōu bù zhīdào
唐僧 你 都 不 知道
Don't you know Tang Monk?

14
00:02:00,442 --> 00:02:02,442
chī dào tángsēngròu kěyǐ chángshēngbùlǎo
吃 到 唐僧肉 可以 长生不老
His flesh can make us be immortal!

15
00:02:02,442 --> 00:02:04,642
tā shì suǒyǒu yāoguài de zhōngjí mèngxiǎng
他 是 所有 妖怪 的 终极 梦想
He is the ultimate dream of all monsters.

16
00:02:05,282 --> 00:02:05,922
zhēnde
真的
Really?!

17
00:02:06,122 --> 00:02:06,802
huózhuō tángsēng
活捉 唐僧
Capture Tang Monk alive!

18
00:02:06,802 --> 00:02:07,322
xū
嘘
Shh!

19
00:02:08,042 --> 00:02:12,242
biǎoxiàn yǒugōng de kěyǐ hē dào yīsháo tángsēng ròutāng
表现 有功 的 可以 喝 到 一勺 唐僧 肉汤
Who has the meritorious performance will get a spoonful of Tang's flesh soup!

20
00:02:12,242 --> 00:02:14,762
dàwáng yīngmíng huózhuō tángsēng
大王 英明 活捉 唐僧
Brilliant! Your Majesty! Capture Tang Monk alive!

21
00:02:20,042 --> 00:02:25,362
míngtiān zhīqián yào zuòchū yīqiān zhījiàn míngbái ma
明天 之前 要 做出 一千 支箭 明白 吗
Make 1,000 arrows by tomorrow! Understand?

22
00:02:42,202 --> 00:02:43,162
zhè yě zhā búzhù ya
这 也 扎 不住 呀
It doesn't work!

23
00:02:43,442 --> 00:02:44,082
nǐ guǎn tā ne
你 管 他 呢
Who cares it!

24
00:02:44,442 --> 00:02:46,282
xióng jiàotóu ràng zěnme zuò zánmen jiù zěnme zuò
熊 教头 让 怎么 做 咱们 就 怎么 做
Let's do what Bear Coach said!

25
00:02:50,162 --> 00:02:51,842
a nǐ gànmá
啊 你 干嘛
Ow! What are you doing?!

26
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:13,720
bào yīqiān zhījiàn yǐjīng zuò wán
报 一千 支箭 已经 做 完
Sir! 1,000 arrows have been made!

27
00:03:25,202 --> 00:03:26,282
nǐ máoní
你 毛呢
Where's your feather?

28
00:03:29,282 --> 00:03:32,122
jiàotóu zhè zhījiàn jiā le yǔmáo ne
教头 这 支箭 加 了 羽毛 呢
Look! Sir! This arrow with feathers,

29
00:03:32,122 --> 00:03:35,242
tā jiù xiàng niǎo yǒu le chìbǎng fēixíng fēicháng wěndìng
它 就 像 鸟 有 了 翅膀 飞行 非常 稳定
it is like a bird with wings, the flight of this arrow is very stable,

30
00:03:35,242 --> 00:03:37,282
mìngzhònglǜ huì dàdàtígāo
命中率 会 大大提高
and the hit rate of it also will be greatly improved!

31
00:03:40,522 --> 00:03:42,602
nǐ zài jiào wǒ zuòshì
你 在 教 我 做事
You're telling me?!

32
00:03:45,242 --> 00:03:48,402
gěi wǒ qù zhòng zuò ànzhào wǒ de fāngfǎ zuò
给 我 去 重 做 按照 我 的 方法 做
Go and redo it according to the approach I told you!

33
00:03:48,402 --> 00:03:51,762
yào yīmúyīyàng bùrán wǒ níngxià nǐ de nǎodài
要 一模一样 不然 我 拧下 你 的 脑袋
Or I'll rip your head off!

34
00:04:00,322 --> 00:04:03,802
nǐ tīngshuō dàwáng zài gǎo yígè tèbié lìhài de jīguān xiànjǐng le ma
你 听说 大王 在 搞 一个 特别 厉害 的 机关 陷阱 了 吗
Hey! Have you heard that our king is working on a particularly powerful trap?

35
00:04:03,962 --> 00:04:05,882
shuō shì yìbǎigè tángsēng dōu pǎobùdiào
说 是 一百个 唐僧 都 跑不掉
Which can never let any prey escape, including Tang Monk?

36
00:04:05,882 --> 00:04:06,722
biéduō dǎtīng le
别多 打听 了
Stop!

37
00:04:07,282 --> 00:04:09,282
nà dōu shì dàwáng hé xiǎo wángmen de shìqíng
那 都 是 大王 和 小 王们 的 事情
That's the business of the king and the little kings,

38
00:04:09,282 --> 00:04:10,762
nǎnéng ràng zánmen zhīdào
哪能 让 咱们 知道
which cannot be known by us!

39
00:04:10,762 --> 00:04:12,722
dàwáng kuījiǎ dào
大王 盔甲 到
Armor of king arrives!

40
00:04:13,002 --> 00:04:15,522
yǒu qǐng sìdà shèngshǒu jìngxǐ
有 请 四大 圣手 净洗
Let's welcome the Four Great Masters to clean up!

41
00:04:15,682 --> 00:04:18,162
nǐ shuō wǒmen shénme shíhòu cáinéng wèi dàwáng cā kuījiǎ ya
你 说 我们 什么 时候 才能 为 大王 擦 盔甲 呀
When do you think we will be able to polish the armor for our king?

42
00:04:18,362 --> 00:04:19,762
nǐ xiǎng tài duō le
你 想 太 多 了
You're overthinking.

43
00:04:19,762 --> 00:04:21,762
qǐmǎ dé xiūliàn sānshínián cáixíng
起码 得 修炼 三十年 才行
We must at least practice for thirty years to do so,

44
00:04:22,002 --> 00:04:24,082
xióng jiàotóu dōu méi zīgé cā ne
熊 教头 都 没 资格 擦 呢
the Bear Coach are not qualified to polish it yet!

45
00:04:25,722 --> 00:04:27,522
nǐ liǎ liáo shénme tiān ne
你 俩 聊 什么 天 呢
What are you two talking about?

46
00:04:27,522 --> 00:04:29,082
guōshuā wán le ma
锅刷 完 了 吗
Have you finished brushing the pot?

47
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,640
hái zhème duōyóu
还 这么 多油
Why are there still so many oil stains?

48
00:04:33,642 --> 00:04:34,802
dàwáng shuō le
大王 说 了
Our king has commanded

49
00:04:34,802 --> 00:04:37,602
zhǔ tángsēngròu de guō bìxū háowú zázhì
煮 唐僧肉 的 锅 必须 毫无 杂质
pot for cooking Tang Monk must be free of impurities

50
00:04:37,602 --> 00:04:39,362
cáinéng bǎozhèng yuánzhīyuánwèi
才能 保证 原汁原味
to ensure the original taste and flavor.

51
00:04:39,362 --> 00:04:40,802
nǐmen cā le bàntiān jiù zhè
你们 擦 了 半天 就 这
You guys brushed half a day on this?

52
00:04:40,802 --> 00:04:43,922
dàrén zhè chénnián lǎoguō yóuzhī zǎn le shàngbǎinián le
大人 这 陈年 老锅 油脂 攒 了 上百年 了
Sir! The grease of this old pot has been saved for hundreds of years.

53
00:04:43,922 --> 00:04:45,362
shízài cābùdiào a
实在 擦不掉 啊
It's really difficult to wipe off!

54
00:04:45,362 --> 00:04:48,522
fèihuà jiù zhè xiǎo pòbù néng cādiào ma
废话 就 这 小 破布 能 擦掉 吗
Shut up! How can you wipe those oil stains off with this small rag?

55
00:04:56,762 --> 00:04:58,002
bàozhù wǒ de shǒu
抱住 我 的 手
Hold my hand.

56
00:05:02,962 --> 00:05:05,242
kànjiàn méiyǒu zhècái jiào shuā guō
看见 没有 这才 叫 刷 锅
Have you seen it? This is the effective pot brushing!

57
00:05:06,042 --> 00:05:07,202
kànjiàn méiyǒu
看见 没有
Have you seen it?

58
00:05:07,202 --> 00:05:10,202
zhè zhūzōng máocái yǒu jìner dé shǐjìn shuā
这 猪鬃 毛才 有 劲儿 得 使劲 刷
his pig bristle is strong, you have to brush hard!

59
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,320
yòng zhège shuā
用 这个 刷
Here, use this!

60
00:05:14,402 --> 00:05:15,322
méiyòng de wányìér
没用 的 玩意儿
You're so pathetic!

61
00:05:15,922 --> 00:05:16,882
wèi nǐ guòlái
喂 你 过来
Hey! You! Come over here!

62
00:05:18,402 --> 00:05:19,922
yòng nàge qù shuā
用 那个 去 刷
Use him to brush!

63
00:05:33,402 --> 00:05:35,562
dàgē máo dōu méi le
大哥 毛 都 没 了
Oh! Ow! Brother! My bristles is going to fall off！

64
00:05:37,082 --> 00:05:39,482
hái kàn shénme cuō máshéng qù
还 看 什么 搓 麻绳 去
What are you looking at? Go to roll the twine!

65
00:05:43,722 --> 00:05:45,280
jīntiān de rènwù fēicháng duō
今天 的 任务 非常 多
a lot of work today,

66
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,640
nǐmen yào fēntóu xíngdòng
你们 要 分头 行动
you have to take action separately.

67
00:05:47,082 --> 00:05:48,402
nǐ qù dānshuǐ
你 去 担水
You! Go to carry water!

68
00:05:48,762 --> 00:05:50,922
nǐ liǎ qù módāo mó bīngqì
你 俩 去 磨刀 磨 兵器
You two! Go to sharpen the weapons!

69
00:05:51,482 --> 00:05:55,122
nǐ liǎ kàn nǐ liǎ zhè tū yàngér
你 俩 看 你 俩 这 秃 样儿
You--Look at you!

70
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,400
nénggàn diǎn shá
能干 点 啥
What the hell can you do?

71
00:05:56,562 --> 00:05:59,962
qù kǎnchái wǎnshàng zhīqián yīqiānjīn
去 砍柴 晚上 之前 一千斤
Go to cut and gather 500kg firewood before night!

72
00:06:07,322 --> 00:06:08,562
yī wǎnshàng yīqiānjīn
一 晚上 一千斤
One night? 500kg?

73
00:06:08,882 --> 00:06:11,362
jiù kào zánliǎ zhèzhā zhā xiǎoyāo zěnme kěnéng
就 靠 咱俩 这渣 渣 小妖 怎么 可能
We two? That's obviously impossible!

74
00:06:14,642 --> 00:06:16,922
zhème kǎn bùxíng dé xiǎngxiǎng bànfǎ
这么 砍 不行 得 想想 办法
No, this is impracticable! We have to do something.

75
00:06:16,922 --> 00:06:18,402
néng yǒu shá bànfǎ
能 有 啥 办法
So, what should we do?

76
00:06:19,122 --> 00:06:19,962
qiǎng
抢
Rob!

77
00:06:20,642 --> 00:06:21,442
qiǎng shuí
抢 谁
Rob who?

78
00:06:21,642 --> 00:06:22,922
qiǎngrén de ya
抢人 的 呀
Human, of course.

79
00:06:23,682 --> 00:06:24,522
duì ya
对 呀
Oh, yes!

80
00:06:25,362 --> 00:06:26,962
wǒmen shì yāoguài ya
我们 是 妖怪 呀
We are monsters!

81
00:07:00,442 --> 00:07:01,362
yāoguài
妖怪
Ah! Ah! Monsters!

82
00:07:04,402 --> 00:07:05,162
biéguòlái
别过来
Get away from me!

83
00:07:05,602 --> 00:07:06,482
biéguòlái
别过来
Get away from me!

84
00:07:07,562 --> 00:07:10,162
yāoguài yéyé yāoguài yéyé ráomìng a
妖怪 爷爷 妖怪 爷爷 饶命 啊
Please, spare my life!

85
00:07:10,162 --> 00:07:12,082
nǐ yào shénme wǒ dōu gěi nǐ
你 要 什么 我 都 给 你
I'll give you whatever you want!

86
00:07:13,082 --> 00:07:14,562
yào nǐ de cháihuǒ
要 你 的 柴火
Give me all of your firewood!

87
00:07:29,042 --> 00:07:31,362
ménsuǒ hǎolema zuìjìn lǎoshì nào yāoguài
门锁 好了吗 最近 老是 闹 妖怪
Did you lock the door? Recently there are always monsters appearing.

88
00:07:31,682 --> 00:07:32,482
suǒhǎo le
锁好 了
Sure!

89
00:07:32,922 --> 00:07:35,202
nǐ tīngshuō le méiyǒu tángsēng guò jǐtiān yào jīngguò zhèlǐ
你 听说 了 没有 唐僧 过 几天 要 经过 这里
Did you hear that Tang Monk will pass through here?

90
00:07:35,682 --> 00:07:39,082
a jiùshì nàge dōngtǔ dàtáng lái de tángsēng
啊 就是 那个 东土 大唐 来 的 唐僧
Who? Is that the monk coming from Tang in the east?

91
00:07:39,082 --> 00:07:41,562
duì ya tā de dà túdì jiào sūnwùkōng
对 呀 他 的 大 徒弟 叫 孙悟空
Yes! One of his disciples is called Sun WuKong,

92
00:07:41,562 --> 00:07:43,522
nà kěshì yígè gàishìyīngxióng
那 可是 一个 盖世英雄
who is the greatest hero in the world.

93
00:07:43,522 --> 00:07:45,442
tiānbīngtiānjiàng dōu ná tā méi bànfǎ
天兵天将 都 拿 他 没 办法
Even the heavenly generals can't do anything with him!

94
00:07:45,602 --> 00:07:47,282
āiyā zhème lìhài a
哎呀 这么 厉害 啊
Really? Is he really so powerful?

95
00:07:47,442 --> 00:07:50,762
yàoshì néng bāng zánmen cūnzi jiàngyāochúmó jiù hǎo le
要是 能 帮 咱们 村子 降妖除魔 就 好 了
It would be great if he could help our village defeat the monsters!

96
00:07:51,082 --> 00:07:53,522
āiyā guǎn nàme duō gànmá shuì ba shuì ba shuì ba
哎呀 管 那么 多 干嘛 睡 吧 睡 吧 睡 吧
Oh, why bother so much? Time to sleep!

97
00:07:57,162 --> 00:07:59,082
bùxíng le bùxíng le lèisǐ le lèisǐ le
不行 了 不行 了 累死 了 累死 了
Oh no, it's really tiring!

98
00:08:00,322 --> 00:08:02,522
chàbuduō gòu le néng jiāochāi le
差不多 够 了 能 交差 了
It is almost enough for us to complete the task.

99
00:08:02,722 --> 00:08:04,202
nǐ tīngshuō guò sūnwùkōng ma
你 听说 过 孙悟空 吗
Have you ever heard of Sun WuKong?

100
00:08:07,202 --> 00:08:09,202
nǐ cāi wǒ jīntiān kàndào le shénme
你 猜 我 今天 看到 了 什么
Guess what I saw today?

101
00:08:09,442 --> 00:08:10,042
shénme
什么
What?

102
00:08:11,042 --> 00:08:12,722
dàwáng bùzhì de xiànjǐng
大王 布置 的 陷阱
The trap laid by our king.

103
00:08:13,402 --> 00:08:14,922
a nà búshì jīmì ma
啊 那 不是 机密 吗
Oh! Isn't that confidential?

104
00:08:15,442 --> 00:08:16,362
xū
嘘
Psst...

105
00:08:16,522 --> 00:08:17,682
nǐ zěnme jìnqù de
你 怎么 进去 的
How did you get in there?

106
00:08:17,682 --> 00:08:19,362
wǒ gāngcái bèizhe cháihuǒ wǎnghuí zǒu
我 刚才 背着 柴火 往回 走
I just walked back with firewood,

107
00:08:19,482 --> 00:08:21,482
lùguò yígè chā zhe cǎiqí yǒu wéidǎng de dìfāng
路过 一个 插 着 彩旗 有 围挡 的 地方
passing a place with the fence made of colored flags.

108
00:08:21,562 --> 00:08:24,442
wǒ hàoqí jiù tōutōu tàntóu kàn le yīyǎn
我 好奇 就 偷偷 探头 看 了 一眼
I was so curious that I peeked in to take a look

109
00:08:24,442 --> 00:08:26,962
ránhòu tīngdào jǐwèi xiǎowáng zài shuō sūnwùkōng de shìér
然后 听到 几位 小王 在 说 孙悟空 的 事儿
and then I heard some little kings were talking about Sun WuKong.

110
00:08:26,962 --> 00:08:30,122
shuō shì dàwáng dǎ bùguò sūnwùkōng cái shèzhì zhège xiànjǐng
说 是 大王 打 不过 孙悟空 才 设置 这个 陷阱
They said that our king couldn't beat Sun WuKong, so they set this trap in advance.

111
00:08:30,322 --> 00:08:32,282
a sūnwùkōng zhēn zhème lìhài
啊 孙悟空 真 这么 厉害
Is Sun WuKong really that powerful?

112
00:08:33,162 --> 00:08:34,560
nà xiànjǐng sháyàng
那 陷阱 啥样
What does that trap look like?

113
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:36,760
wǒ kàn bù tài dǒng dàn gǎnjué tǐngqiáng de
我 看 不 太 懂 但 感觉 挺强 的
I don't know much about it, but it looks pretty powerful...

114
00:08:37,002 --> 00:08:39,842
láng dàrén zhèbiān qǐng zhèbiān qǐng
狼 大人 这边 请 这边 请
This way please, Lord Wolf.

115
00:08:40,322 --> 00:08:45,680
nín kàn zhèshì wǒmen wèidùn tángsēng zhǔnbèi de cháihuǒ gòng yīqiānjīn
您 看 这是 我们 为炖 唐僧 准备 的 柴火 共 一千斤
Look, this is the firewood we prepared for cooking Tang Monk, a total of 500kg,

116
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:48,680
kěyǐ zuòdào huǒ sāntiānsānyè bù miè
可以 做到 火 三天三夜 不 灭
which can keep the fire burning in three days and nights!

117
00:09:16,842 --> 00:09:18,642
dàrén ráomìng dàrén ráomìng a
大人 饶命 大人 饶命 啊
Spare me! Please, Lord! Please!

118
00:09:18,642 --> 00:09:20,082
láng dàrén zhèshì wèihé
狼 大人 这是 为何
Lord? Why?

119
00:09:20,082 --> 00:09:23,362
xiǎoxiǎo yāoguài jìnggǎn shànchuǎng jīmì zhòngdì
小小 妖怪 竟敢 擅闯 机密 重地
How dare he trespass on the secret place?

120
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:26,200
dàwáng bùzhì de xiànjǐng qǐnéng ràng ěr děng zhīdào
大王 布置 的 陷阱 岂能 让 尔 等 知道
How can you little ones know about the trap the king set?

121
00:09:26,402 --> 00:09:28,962
xiǎorén bùzhī guǎnjiào bùyán
小人 不知 管教 不严
It's my fault! I don't know!

122
00:09:28,962 --> 00:09:30,322
qǐng dàrén shùzuì
请 大人 恕罪
Forgive me!

123
00:09:32,722 --> 00:09:33,522
dàrén
大人
My lord?

124
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,560
dàwáng gānggāng gǎile zhǔyì
大王 刚刚 改了 主意
Our king changed his plan just now!

125
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,960
tángsēng yào kǎo zhe chī
唐僧 要 烤 着 吃
He will roast the flesh of Tang Monk instead of boiling!

126
00:09:37,122 --> 00:09:39,162
zhèxiē pǔtōng cháihuǒ zāotà wèidào
这些 普通 柴火 糟蹋 味道
This common firewood will spoil the flavor of the flesh of Tang!

127
00:09:39,522 --> 00:09:42,762
mǎshàng qù cǎi liǎngqiānjīn èrshínián yǐxià de shān hútáomù
马上 去 采 两千斤 二十年 以下 的 山 胡桃木
Prepare 1,000kg hickory wood under twenty years, rewove the peel and wash it!

128
00:09:42,762 --> 00:09:46,162
qùpí xǐjìng liànggān hòutiān zhǔnbèi tuǒdàng
去皮 洗净 晾干 后天 准备 妥当
All of this must be done before the day after tomorrow!

129
00:09:46,322 --> 00:09:47,282
bùdéyǒuwù
不得有误
Understand?

130
00:09:47,282 --> 00:09:48,242
shì
是
Yes! Lord!

131
00:09:54,522 --> 00:09:58,002
yī wǎnshàng jiù cǎi le liǎngbǎijīn hái xiǎng bùxiǎng huó le
一 晚上 就 采 了 两百斤 还 想 不想 活 了
Just 100kg? One night? Do you want to live or not?

132
00:09:58,362 --> 00:10:00,042
míngtiān tángsēng jiù dào le
明天 唐僧 就 到 了
Tomorrow! Tang Monk will arrive here!

133
00:10:00,042 --> 00:10:01,482
nǐmen jiù zhè zhuàngtài
你们 就 这 状态
Look at your lethargic appearance!

134
00:10:02,002 --> 00:10:04,602
jīntiān tiānhēi zhīqián rúguǒ cǎi búdào liǎngqiānjīn
今天 天黑 之前 如果 采 不到 两千斤
Before dark, if you do not pick 1,000kg,

135
00:10:04,922 --> 00:10:06,682
wǒ tōngtōng bǎ nǐmen qù wèiyú
我 通通 把 你们 去 喂鱼
I will take you to feed fish!

136
00:10:07,322 --> 00:10:08,402
kuàiqù gànhuó
快去 干活
Go to work! Hurry up!

137
00:10:11,922 --> 00:10:12,682
nǐ zhànzhù
你 站住
Hey! you!

138
00:10:13,602 --> 00:10:14,602
gěinǐgè rènwù
给你个 任务
Another task for you!

139
00:10:14,802 --> 00:10:18,482
qù zhènzi lǐ mǎi wǔshíjīn yán sānshíjīn zīrán èrshíjīn huājiāo
去 镇子 里 买 五十斤 盐 三十斤 孜然 二十斤 花椒
Go to the town! Buy me 25kg salt, 15kg cumin seed, and 10kg Sichuan pepper.

140
00:10:18,482 --> 00:10:19,882
búyào jiéwàishēngzhī
不要 节外生枝
Remember! Don't make new trouble!

141
00:10:26,922 --> 00:10:30,560
lǎobǎn lái wǔshíjīn yán sānshíjīn zīrán èrshíjīn huājiāo
老板 来 五十斤 盐 三十斤 孜然 二十斤 花椒
Excuse me! 25kg salt, 15kg cumin seed, and 10kg Sichuan pepper, please.

142
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,360
hǎolēi
好勒
Okay!

143
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,720
kèguān zhè shì zuò fànguǎn shēngyì de ba
客官 这 是 做 饭馆 生意 的 吧
You are in the restaurant business, right?

144
00:10:35,642 --> 00:10:37,762
è lǎobǎn nǐ tīngshuō guò tángsēng ma
呃 老板 你 听说 过 唐僧 吗
Uh...Have you heard of the Tang Monk?

145
00:10:38,162 --> 00:10:39,402
dāngrán le
当然 了
Of course!

146
00:10:39,642 --> 00:10:41,680
xuánzàngfǎshī dǐngdǐngdàmíng a
玄奘法师 鼎鼎大名 啊
Eminent Monk Xuan Zang from Tang dynasty! That is known to everybody.

147
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,640
tāzhǎng shénmeyàng
他长 什么样
What does he look like?

148
00:10:42,722 --> 00:10:43,682
wǒ kě méi jiàn guò
我 可 没 见 过
I've never seen him before.

149
00:10:44,922 --> 00:10:46,802
nǐ kěyǐ wènwèn shuōshū de nàge
你 可以 问问 说书 的 那个
Hmmm...you may ask the storyteller,

150
00:10:47,402 --> 00:10:49,722
tā měitiān shuō tángsēng shītú sìrén de gùshì
他 每天 说 唐僧 师徒 四人 的 故事
He always tells stories of Tang Monk and his three disciples

151
00:10:50,322 --> 00:10:51,642
jiù zài qiánmiàn nàge guǎijiǎo
就 在 前面 那个 拐角
in front of that corner!

152
00:10:52,042 --> 00:10:55,680
shītú sìrén zì dōngtǔ dàtáng ér lái
师徒 四人 自 东土 大唐 而 来
Tang Monk and his three disciples come from Tang in the east，

153
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,680
qùwǎng xītiān qǔjīng
去往 西天 取经
and they go west to worship the Buddha.

154
00:10:57,962 --> 00:11:02,082
huà shuō zhè sān túdì shāhéshàng shēnxíng jiànshuò
话 说 这 三 徒弟 沙和尚 身形 健硕
It is said that Tang Monk's third disciple Sandy has a strong body,

155
00:11:02,122 --> 00:11:03,442
zhǎngxū nóngméi
长须 浓眉
with a long beard

156
00:11:03,442 --> 00:11:06,242
shǒuchí de shì jiàngyāo bǎozhàng
手持 的 是 降妖 宝杖
and heavy eyebrows on his face and with ogre−quelling staff in his hand.

157
00:11:06,602 --> 00:11:08,962
èr túdì zhūbājiè shēngāo sānzhàng
二 徒弟 猪八戒 身高 三丈
Pigsy, the second disciple of Tang Monk, thirty feet tall,

158
00:11:09,122 --> 00:11:10,442
zhǎngbí dàěr
长鼻 大耳
with long nose and big ears,

159
00:11:10,442 --> 00:11:12,282
shǒuchí de shì jiǔchǐ dīngpá
手持 的 是 九齿 钉耙
hold a nine-pronged rake in hand.

160
00:11:13,202 --> 00:11:17,362
tángsānzàng shēng dé shì méiqīngmùxiù yīliǎn fóxiàng
唐三藏 生 得 是 眉清目秀 一脸 佛像
As for Tang Monk himself. He has a beautiful face and just like Buddha.

161
00:11:17,882 --> 00:11:20,402
zài kàn zhèdà túdì sūnwùkōng
再 看 这大 徒弟 孙悟空
And finally, let's talk about his oldest disciple Sun WuKong,

162
00:11:20,402 --> 00:11:22,242
hàochēng qítiāndàshèng
号称 齐天大圣
known as Great Sage Equaling Heaven;

163
00:11:22,522 --> 00:11:25,442
shíwàn tiānbīngtiānjiàng ná tā nàihé bùdé
十万 天兵天将 拿 他 奈何 不得
One hundred thousand heavenly generals can't do anything with him.

164
00:11:25,882 --> 00:11:29,242
zhēn nǎi gàishìyīngxióng a
真 乃 盖世英雄 啊
He is a real hero!

165
00:11:34,122 --> 00:11:35,122
shīfù
师傅
Excuse me! Maestro!

166
00:11:35,482 --> 00:11:38,162
wǒ xiǎng wènwèn tángsēng zhège rén zěnmeyàng a
我 想 问问 唐僧 这个 人 怎么样 啊
I would like to ask how about this person, Tang Monk?

167
00:11:38,242 --> 00:11:41,082
tángsānzàng xíngshàn hǎoshī wèimínchúhài
唐三藏 行善 好施 为民除害
Tang Monk, a charitable and philanthropic genius of the millennium,

168
00:11:41,082 --> 00:11:43,242
shì qiānnián bùyù de fǎshī a
是 千年 不遇 的 法师 啊
exterminates evils for our human beings!

169
00:11:43,602 --> 00:11:44,682
zhème hǎo
这么 好
Is he really so good?

170
00:11:45,042 --> 00:11:45,922
nà kěbù
那 可不
That's for sure!

171
00:11:46,042 --> 00:11:48,202
yàobùrán sūndàshèng nàme dà néngnài de yāoguài
要不然 孙大圣 那么 大 能耐 的 妖怪
Otherwise, Sun WuKong,

172
00:11:48,202 --> 00:11:50,962
bù kěnéng guāiguāi dì gēn tā qù xītiān qǔjīng a
不 可能 乖乖 地 跟 他 去 西天 取经 啊
such a capable monster cannot be convinced to follow him!

173
00:11:51,322 --> 00:11:52,602
sūndàshèng yě shì yāoguài
孙大圣 也 是 妖怪
Is Sun WuKong also a monster?

174
00:11:53,042 --> 00:11:53,762
duì ya
对 呀
Uh huh!

175
00:11:53,882 --> 00:11:55,682
sūndàshèng jiùshì gè hóuzi
孙大圣 就是 个 猴子
Sun WuKong is a monkey.

176
00:11:55,962 --> 00:11:57,402
zhūbājiè yě shì zhǐ zhū yāo
猪八戒 也 是 只 猪 妖
Pigsy is a pig.

177
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,840
hòulái dōu bèi tángsēng shōu le qù zuò túdì
后来 都 被 唐僧 收 了 去 做 徒弟
Sun Wukong and Pigsy are both willing to become disciples of Tang Monk.

178
00:12:00,082 --> 00:12:05,282
suǒyǐ tángsēng zhēnshì cíbēiwèihuái pǔdùzhòngshēng a
所以 唐僧 真是 慈悲为怀 普度众生 啊
Tang Monk helps countless beings, and he is very mercyful.

179
00:12:07,322 --> 00:12:09,802
（ lùpái ） dàwáng dòng
（ 路牌 ） 大王 洞
(on the signboard) Da Wang cave

180
00:12:28,322 --> 00:12:29,402
māmā
妈妈
Mom!

181
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:33,200
mā zhè dōngxī jiào bāozi wǒgāng zài zhènshàng mǎi de
妈 这 东西 叫 包子 我刚 在 镇上 买 的
Mom! This is steamed stuffed bun, I just bought in market town,

182
00:12:33,362 --> 00:12:35,162
nǐ hé dìdi mèimèi men chángcháng
你 和 弟弟 妹妹 们 尝尝
you and my siblings can have a taste.

183
00:12:37,242 --> 00:12:37,882
hǎochī
好吃
Yum! Yummy!

184
00:12:37,882 --> 00:12:38,522
wǒ yě yào
我 也 要
Give me one too!

185
00:12:39,482 --> 00:12:40,042
hǎochī
好吃
Yum! Yummy!

186
00:12:40,042 --> 00:12:41,322
gěi māmā liú yīkuài
给 妈妈 留 一块
Save some for mom!

187
00:12:41,322 --> 00:12:44,122
dōu ràng tāmen chī le ba zhǎng shēntǐ
都 让 他们 吃 了 吧 长 身体
Just let them eat. They are growing up and need nutrition.

188
00:12:44,882 --> 00:12:45,802
nǐ zěnmeyàng
你 怎么样
How's the world treating you?

189
00:12:45,802 --> 00:12:48,202
yīnián dōu méi huílái shìbúshì tàimáng le
一年 都 没 回来 是不是 太忙 了
You haven't been back for a year, have you been too busy?

190
00:12:48,442 --> 00:12:49,162
duì duì duì
对 对 对
Yeah, yeah, yeah!

191
00:12:49,482 --> 00:12:52,882
xiànzài dàwáng gěi wǒ pài le hěnduō shìqíng měitiān zuò dōu zuò bù wán
现在 大王 给 我 派 了 很多 事情 每天 做 都 做 不 完
Now the king gives me a lot of things to do every day.

192
00:12:53,082 --> 00:12:54,442
dàwáng zhòngshì nǐ jiù hǎo
大王 重视 你 就 好
It's good that the king likes you!

193
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,480
xiǎngdāngchū dàwáng pàirénlái tiāo
想当初 大王 派人来 挑
I always remember the king sent someone to pick.

194
00:12:56,642 --> 00:12:59,680
nǐ zài ménkǒu wán yīxiàzi jiù bèi xuǎnzhōng
你 在 门口 玩 一下子 就 被 选中
You were immediately selected when you were playing at the door.

195
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:03,120
zájiā shàngxià sāndài zhōngyú chū le gè réncái
咱家 上下 三代 终于 出 了 个 人才
I'm so proud of you! Our family has finally produced a talent for three generations!

196
00:13:06,322 --> 00:13:07,762
nǐ yě búyào tàipīn le
你 也 不要 太拼 了
Oh dear! You don't have to work so hard either...

197
00:13:08,202 --> 00:13:08,722
a
啊
What?

198
00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:11,562
nǐ kànkàn nǐ zěnme tūchéng zhèyàng
你 看看 你 怎么 秃成 这样
Look at you! You're going bald!

199
00:13:12,322 --> 00:13:15,722
ō ō ō zuìjìn lǎo áoyè máodiào dé lìhài
噢 噢 噢 最近 老 熬夜 毛掉 得 厉害
Ow-ow-ow, Recently I always stay up late, so that I lost a lot of my bristles.

200
00:13:16,282 --> 00:13:18,802
nǐ dé xuéhuì zhàogù zìjǐ biétàilèi le
你 得 学会 照顾 自己 别太累 了
You should learn to take good care of yourself and not get too tired.

201
00:13:23,042 --> 00:13:25,282
nǐ kànkàn wǒ cāi jiùshì kōng de
你 看看 我 猜 就是 空 的
I thought as much! I guessed it was empty, and it was!

202
00:13:25,282 --> 00:13:26,682
jiùshì bùài hēshuǐ
就是 不爱 喝水
Why do you dislike drinking water?!

203
00:13:27,282 --> 00:13:30,442
nǐ xiǎoshíhòu ài késòu māmā cái gěi nǐ dài de zhège húlú
你 小时候 爱 咳嗽 妈妈 才 给 你 带 的 这个 葫芦
I gave you this bottle gourd because you usually coughed when you were a little kid.

204
00:13:30,922 --> 00:13:33,122
jiùshì xiǎng ràng nǐ duōhēshuǐ bié shànghuǒ
就是 想 让 你 多喝水 别 上火
I hope that you can drink water frequently to avoid illness.

205
00:13:33,522 --> 00:13:34,802
nǐ jiùshì bù tīng
你 就是 不 听
But you always forget what I told you!

206
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:38,520
āi nǐ zhè yígè rén zài wàibiān yě méiyǒu rén zhàogù
哎 你 这 一个 人 在 外边 也 没有 人 照顾
Oh boy, there's no one to take care of you when you are not at home.

207
00:13:40,122 --> 00:13:41,522
wǒ xiǎng líkāi lànglàngshān
我 想 离开 浪浪山
I want to leave Wave Mountain...

208
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:42,440
nǐ shuō shá
你 说 啥
What are you talking about?

209
00:13:42,522 --> 00:13:45,282
wǒ zài xiǎng gēnzhe dàwáng shì tǐng hǎo
我 在 想 跟着 大王 是 挺 好
I'm just thinking that it is indeed good to follow the king,

210
00:13:45,642 --> 00:13:48,762
kěshì zhè yībèizi dài zài lànglàngshān yě shì wúqù
可是 这 一辈子 待 在 浪浪山 也 是 无趣
but staying in the Wave Mountain all my life is also boring.

211
00:13:49,162 --> 00:13:50,882
shìbúshì gāi chūqù chuǎng chuǎng
是不是 该 出去 闯 闯
Should I go out into the world?

212
00:13:50,882 --> 00:13:52,442
āi biéxiāxiǎng
哎 别瞎想
come on! Don't be silly!

213
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:54,200
néng yǒu gè gàndé bùcuò le
能 有 个 干得 不错 了
It is lucky for you to have this job!

214
00:13:54,482 --> 00:13:57,602
nǐ gēnzhe dàwáng hǎohǎo gàn zhēngqǔ zǎorì xiūliàn chéngjīng
你 跟着 大王 好好 干 争取 早日 修炼 成精
You should work hard with the king and strive to become excellent as soon as possible!

215
00:13:57,762 --> 00:13:59,002
zhècái shì zhèngshì
这才 是 正事
That's the most important thing!

216
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:08,880
kàndào méiyǒu zhèshì jīntiān tángsēng shītú sìrén bìjīngzhīlù
看到 没有 这是 今天 唐僧 师徒 四人 必经之路
The day of Tang Monk's arrival
See, this is the road Tang Monk and his disciples must go through today.

217
00:14:09,442 --> 00:14:13,762
běnlái zhè tiáo lù shì zhí de dàwáng bǎ zhè tiáolù zài nàlǐ gǎi le gè dào
本来 这 条 路 是 直 的 大王 把 这 条路 在 那里 改 了 个 道
Originally this road is straight, our king changed it.

218
00:14:13,962 --> 00:14:17,322
tāmen sìgè jiù huì yánzhe zhè tiáo lù zǒujìn nàpiàn shùlín lǐ
他们 四个 就 会 沿着 这 条 路 走进 那片 树林 里
They will walk along this road into the woods

219
00:14:17,322 --> 00:14:20,042
jīguān jiù zài nàge zuìgāo de shù xiàmiàn
机关 就 在 那个 最高 的 树 下面
The secret trap is under the tallest tree.

220
00:14:20,042 --> 00:14:22,082
tángsēng jiù huì zài nàlǐ bèi dàwáng zhuāzhù
唐僧 就 会 在 那里 被 大王 抓住
Tang Monk will be caught by our King there!

221
00:14:22,202 --> 00:14:23,922
zánmen zài zhèlǐ gōngjiàn máifú
咱们 在 这里 弓箭 埋伏
We are here in ambush with bows and arrows.

222
00:14:23,922 --> 00:14:27,722
jiùshì yǐfángwànyī yǒurén táotuō zài zhè jiāng qí qínná
就是 以防万一 有人 逃脱 在 这 将 其 擒拿
If someone try to escape, catch him here.

223
00:14:30,762 --> 00:14:33,322
xióng jiàotóu wūyā guài hái méi huílái ma
熊 教头 乌鸦 怪 还 没 回来 吗
Bear Coach, Haven't the crow come back yet?

224
00:14:33,802 --> 00:14:36,922
huílái bèi láng dàrén zhuāzǒu hái néng huílái
回来 被 狼 大人 抓走 还 能 回来
Back? Can you come back after being captured by Lord Wolf?

225
00:14:51,562 --> 00:14:53,642
xióng jiàotóu wǒ qù sā pào niào
熊 教头 我 去 撒 泡 尿
Bear Coach, I'll go pee.

226
00:14:54,002 --> 00:14:57,122
lǎnlǘ shàng mó shǐniào duō kuàiqùkuàihuí
懒驴 上 磨 屎尿 多 快去快回
Drop away at critical moment! Go back quickly!

227
00:15:28,122 --> 00:15:29,362
nǐ zài zhè gànshénme
你 在 这 干什么
What are you doing here?

228
00:15:30,082 --> 00:15:31,402
méishénme méishénme
没什么 没什么
No-nothing!

229
00:15:31,402 --> 00:15:32,522
wǒ wǒ jiùshì sāniào lùguò
我 我 就是 撒尿 路过
I-I-I am just passing by peeing...

230
00:15:35,962 --> 00:15:36,762
gěi wǒ zhànzhù
给 我 站住
Stop right there!

231
00:16:28,842 --> 00:16:30,202
a a a
啊 啊 啊
Ah!!!

232
00:18:07,162 --> 00:18:11,722
biéguòlái biéguòlái
别过来 别过来
Don't come any closer! Don't come over!

233
00:18:11,722 --> 00:18:16,322
zhèlǐ yǒu wēixiǎn
这里 有 危险
It's dangerous here!

234
00:18:42,282 --> 00:18:45,242
wùkōng nà xiǎoyāo gāngcái zài hǎn shénme
悟空 那 小妖 刚才 在 喊 什么
Sun WuKong, what was the little monster shouting?

235
00:18:45,842 --> 00:18:50,322
shīfù guǎn tā hǎn shénme yāoguài yī bàngzi dǎsǐ biàn kě
师父 管 他 喊 什么 妖怪 一 棒子 打死 便 可
Master, it's nothing! Just a little monster, just sent him to death.

236
00:19:05,282 --> 00:19:10,282
gǎnxiè tángzhǎnglǎo wèi běncūn jiàngyāochúmó
感谢 唐长老 为 本村 降妖除魔
Thank you, Tang Monk, for getting rid of the monsters in our village.

237
00:19:11,042 --> 00:19:14,122
yào gǎnxiè jiù gǎnxiè wǒ de jǐgè túdì ba
要 感谢 就 感谢 我 的 几个 徒弟 吧
That's all right, thanks to my disciples.

238
00:19:15,002 --> 00:19:18,322
lǎo cūnzhǎng nǐ zhèlǐ de yāoguài tàiruò le
老 村长 你 这里 的 妖怪 太弱 了
Chief, monsters in your village are too weak.

239
00:19:18,642 --> 00:19:22,122
dōu bùyòng ǎn lǎosūn dòngshǒu bājiè jiù quán gǎodìng le
都 不用 俺 老孙 动手 八戒 就 全 搞定 了
There is no need for me to do it. Pigsy handled it all by himself.

240
00:19:22,242 --> 00:19:28,522
duì ya nàge shénme dàwáng háiyào gǎo yígè jīguān xiànjǐng gēn dòu xiǎohái shìde
对 呀 那个 什么 大王 还要 搞 一个 机关 陷阱 跟 逗 小孩 似的
Right! The trap their king set was just like a kidding.

241
00:19:28,642 --> 00:19:31,562
háiyǒu yībāng shénme báimáo lángzá máoxióng shá de
还有 一帮 什么 白毛 狼杂 毛熊 啥 的
And his members, like the white wolf, the poor bear and many others!

242
00:19:31,562 --> 00:19:35,842
dōu bèi ǎn lǎozhū de dīngpá yī hūlū quánsòng shàng le xītiān hāhāhā
都 被 俺 老猪 的 钉耙 一 呼噜 全送 上 了 西天 哈哈哈
All are killed by my nine-pronged rake. Hahaha...

243
00:19:36,962 --> 00:19:40,722
chúle nà zhǐ xiǎozhū yāo ǎn dào shì fàng le tā yītiáo shēnglù
除了 那 只 小猪 妖 俺 倒 是 放 了 他 一条 生路
In addition to the little pig, I left him alive.

244
00:19:40,882 --> 00:19:43,242
búshì yī bàngzi dǎsǐ le ma
不是 一 棒子 打死 了 吗
You didn't kill him?

245
00:19:43,522 --> 00:19:46,642
dāizi dāngshí nà xiǎozhū bèi báimáo láng zhuī zhe
呆子 当时 那 小猪 被 白毛 狼 追 着
Idiot! I pretended to hit him.

246
00:19:46,642 --> 00:19:49,322
zhè bàngzi shì yǎngěi tāmen kàn
这 棒子 是 演给 他们 看
Because the white wolf was after him to kill him.

247
00:19:49,322 --> 00:19:52,202
xiǎozhū hǎn de yǒu máifú ǎn tīng dé yìqīngèrchǔ
小猪 喊 的 有 埋伏 俺 听 得 一清二楚
I heard clearly what the little pig was shouting.

248
00:19:52,202 --> 00:19:54,242
zhè jiào jiāngjìjiùjì
这 叫 将计就计
This is called counterplot!

249
00:19:54,242 --> 00:19:56,360
bùrán zhèbāng yāoguài háigǎn chūlái
不然 这帮 妖怪 还敢 出来
Otherwise, these monsters still dare to come out?

250
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:58,680
zánmen hái zěnme gěi dāngdì chúhài
咱们 还 怎么 给 当地 除害
How else can we get rid of them?

251
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:16,040
zhè sāngēn shì bǎomìng háomáo nǐ bǎ tā shōu hǎo yǐhòu yòngdézhe
这 三根 是 保命 毫毛 你 把 它 收 好 以后 用得着
Take this! It is my fur which can save your life in the future
